<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得年末的時候，<delay8 />總是匆匆忙忙的呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />迎接新年的準備工作，<delay20 />
你都做好了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你問我嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是打算趕在跨年的倒數派對之前，
把事情都做完啦……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你已經去廣場看過了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了跨年倒數，<delay8 />大家都如火如荼地在準備呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然正式的倒數是從11點才開始的，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過看到大家這麼起勁，<delay8 />你不覺得
跨年的氣氛也更熱鬧了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />過了今天，這一年就要結束了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後<tag a="90" b="27" />年<delay8 />
就會離我而遠去<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />新的一年也會到來，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我一點也不寂寞喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跨年的倒數派對，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會來參加嗎？<delay20 />還是不會參加？<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然你很忙的話，<delay8 />不用勉強來也沒關係的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我說不定<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
會忍不住在人群中<delay8 />
到處尋找你的身影呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>